# AI Agent Instructions & Workspace Rules

Welcome! This repository uses a modular rules architecture. Rules and system constraints are dynamically triggered by the agent runner and are stored individually in the [`.agents/rules/`](file:///C:/Users/Yosua%20Jan/.gemini/antigravity/worktrees/final-finance-family/redesign-ui-supabase-stack/.agents/rules) directory.

Adhere strictly to all workspace rules outlined below and defined in the modular rule files.

---

